            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01WyWsuLs6FMtSe2Y2VjyeBv\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Great question! After you launch your site, you'll have a live landing page that you can share with potential customers. You can share the link anywhere - social media, email campaigns, your podcast, etc. The page will be hosted and ready to collect leads or drive conversions. Plus, you can always come back to edit and update your page whenever you want - nothing is set in stone. Want to build it now and see what we've created?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4066,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":117,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
