            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01S6AvhbAcojBj5zwGx5d7JH\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"helpMe\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Great question! Let me help you break this down into clear pieces.\\\",\\n  \\\"template\\\": \\\"**Who are they?**\\\\n[Role/title] at [type/size of company or context] who [key characteristic about their situation]\\\\n\\\\n**What problems do they face?**\\\\n• [Specific frustration #1 related to finding/booking guests]\\\\n• [Specific frustration #2 about time/effort]\\\\n• [Emotional impact - how does this make them feel?]\\\\n\\\\n**What are they trying to achieve?**\\\\n• [Immediate goal for their podcast]\\\\n• [Bigger goal - what success looks like]\\\\n\\\\n**Why don't current solutions work?** (optional)\\\\n[What they've tried and why it falls short]\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"**Who are they?** Podcast hosts of business/marketing shows with 500-10K downloads per episode who are producing weekly content but don't have a full-time producer.\\\\n\\\\n**What problems do they face?**\\\\n• Spend 3-5 hours per week cold-emailing potential guests with low response rates\\\\n• Struggle to find guests who are actually relevant and engaging (not just willing)\\\\n• Feel anxious about content calendar gaps when guests cancel or don't respond\\\\n\\\\n**What are they trying to achieve?**\\\\n• Consistently book high-quality guests who bring fresh insights their audience will love\\\\n• Grow their show's credibility and download numbers by featuring respected voices\\\\n\\\\n**Why don't current solutions work?**\\\\nGuest booking agencies are expensive ($500+/guest) and LinkedIn outreach is time-consuming with hit-or-miss results.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3039,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":409,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
