            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01WbgZsRxNoHdMfXBQXx28wg\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I can see you're clarifying your target audience, which is helpful context! However, I'm specifically asking about **social proof** - things that build credibility and trust for your service.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Let me ask more directly: What makes YOU credible to deliver this service? Do you have any proof that Friend of the Pod works?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Your own experience in podcasting or building marketplaces\\\",\\n    \\\"Early testimonials from beta users\\\",\\n    \\\"Number of matches made or success stories\\\",\\n    \\\"Your expertise in AI/tech that powers the matching\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"If you don't have formal testimonials yet, that's okay - we can skip this and move on. Just let me know!\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3017,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":186,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
