            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1264,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01D2qfkK9CmREMEtMpEd1gkM\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I don't see any uploaded images yet. But don't worry—you can upload images when we move to the design phase!\\n\\nWe still need to cover one more topic: **the look and feel** for your landing page.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Let's talk about the visual style and tone for your landing page. What kind of look and feel do you want?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Modern and minimal with lots of white space—think Apple or Stripe\\\",\\n    \\\"Bold and energetic with bright colors—podcasting is fun and creative\\\",\\n    \\\"Professional and trustworthy—dark blues and clean typography, like a SaaS tool\\\",\\n    \\\"Warm and community-focused—friendly colors and approachable design\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What vibe should your landing page have? Think about colors, style, and the overall feeling you want to convey.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3087,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":214,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
